description:
Receiving a new name, http://anidb.net/ch117168 [Bond] joins the Moriarty ranks, and is sent to retrieve the contents of a safe deposit box with Moran, Louis, and Fred. But when an unexpected bank heist spurs the others into spontaneous action, Bond is left wondering what to do.
Source: Funimation

titles.title: ホワイトチャペルの亡霊 第一幕
